{"tid":111923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魁北克擬設合法吸毒室 加拿大衛生部批准","createTime":"2017-02-07T17:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T18:07:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f35b3a07126bb679123b2ad8220102bf11b40f3c","tid":111923,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T17:42:47.000Z","msg":"<strong>魁北克擬設合法吸毒室 加國衛生部批准</strong><br />\n<br />\n時間：2017-02-07 12:28 新聞引據：中央社<br />\n<br />\n加拿大衛生部長6日批准十多年來北美首間新的合法吸毒室，以努力抑制毒品吸食過量危機。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部長菲爾波特(Jane Philpott)同意了來自魁北克省公共衛生機構所提的申請。魁北克的公衛機構計畫於蒙特婁市中心的Hochelaga-Maisonneuve，以及Ville-Marie近郊開設3處吸毒室。<br />\n<br />\n菲爾波特在一項聲明裡說：「設立有監控的合法吸毒點，在加拿大及其他國家已顯現正面結果；疾病散播與吸毒過量致死案降低，與注射毒品所衍生的感染、急診和住院也都減少」。<br />\n<br />\n北美第一間又稱為「監管下毒品注射室」的吸毒室，是2003年依據聯邦毒品持有和販運相關法律所給予的特殊豁免，設於鄰近溫哥華市中心東邊的一間診所。<br />\n<br />\n渥太華、多倫多和其他數個加拿大城市也在考慮開辦類似據點。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=324553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F%3FrecordId%3D324553&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=2fcf8a01\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=324553</a><br />\n<br />\n&rarr; ddd1935: 葡萄牙之前也是禁止，但合法化之後吸毒人數大幅下降<br />\n<br />\n推 supertalker: 合法後非法的就少人買啊，這麼簡單的道理政府自己賺<br />\n<br />\n推 tentaikanso: 吸毒跟販毒不同，吸毒更像是疾病而非犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n推 DavidEaston: 台灣明智未開  一堆老人一定會出來扭曲 <br />\n<br />\n推 tentaikanso: 而且這些毒品室除了提供「安全衛生」的毒品外，也可 <br />\n&rarr; tentaikanso: 以達到辨認吸毒者並協助戒治的效果，也能有效打擊非  <br />\n&rarr; tentaikanso: 法/地下毒品市場，<strong>成本說不定還比掃毒、跟毒犯槍戰低</strong><br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1486443374.A.E3D.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1486443374.A.E3D.html&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=979910d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1486443374.A.E3D.html</a>"},{"pid":"06e03609da99f513959b14669ba6a6947e07d075","tid":111923,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T19:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee9db742e2dc0df0e34416b9c8be39a9d05c2bd","tid":111923,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa7e9012578dc51a43a950b2e7f885d87014886","tid":111923,"uid":7620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:17:37.000Z","msg":"Transporting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a7dc6841160ac443bcf9cb3ffb38af9295fbc2","tid":111923,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a65e7dc644aa13cacc6a41c7929d47c3cf6ad4","tid":111923,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"193x年美國禁酒，結果：當時酒=依家嘅毒品，有走私有私製有炒高，有啲黑幫因而崛起<br />\n<br />\n結果：美國取消禁酒"},{"pid":"2fe3ee3f4c162cad4f4156653f7ad4161e0ea9c5","tid":111923,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"左到就黎痴線"},{"pid":"3466ad0bcfc313f46eb22099b1b23f5ee60da585","tid":111923,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"新戰鬥民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吸完毒唔怕凍"},{"pid":"2c2867d4cae4b69e3ace88df885bfbc5bf89fb5e","tid":111923,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"吸咩毒先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fd65d9e3a546318b2c4dc57f47c55b97ecaebc","tid":111923,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左到就黎痴線</blockquote><br />\n唔關左唔左事<br />\n事關政府預算同社會成本問題<br />\n你拉人坐監、掃毒、維護治